headline: T-Mobile Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: BELLEVUE, Wash., November 21, 2024--T-Mobile US, Inc. (NASDAQ: TMUS) ("T-Mobile" or "the Company") announced today that the Company’s Board of Directors has declared a cash dividend of $0.88 per share on its issued and outstanding shares of common stock. The dividend is payable on March 13, 2025 to stockholders of record as of the close of business on February 28, 2025.
